    "body": "Hey @drortirosh , I notice the truffle config in the referenced repo doesn't include the new config setting for speedy parsing.\r\n\r\nFor reference from #2067 :\r\n\r\n>To enable speedy JS parsing, users will need to specify a `parser: \"solcjs\"` key/value pair in their config like so:\r\n\r\n```\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  compilers: {\r\n    solc: {\r\n      parser: \"solcjs\"\r\n    }\r\n  }  \r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nHope this helps!",
